<br>
Caillou, wood elf worshipper or Tunare, couldn't imagine giving or selling an item to a dark elf even if he purported to be good (at least at this point in her life).  However, if it was a human, she would have no issue with it at all, even if that human was actually a shadow knight worshiper of Innouruk because she would have no way to discern that on appearance alone.  What does she know (still young) of shadow knight only items or armor (ooc: even if I did inpect &amp; see something, I would have to look on spoiler sites to know what 90% of the items are anyway)?  If the human is wearing plate (or what looks to be plate) and wielding a sword or two, he could be either a warrior or paladin (but Caillou has been learning that humans are confusing and could be evil as easily as good).<br>
